Name: Run Star Motion CX Platform Workwear High Top
Description: COLOUR THE FUTURE Reflecting the energy of city streets, the Run Star Motion's playful and distorted lines are built for future movement. Reimagined from the inside out, the elevated stance and CX foam midsole help bring next-level comfort to every stride. The upper stays true to the original, juxtaposed by future-forward design details for bold self-expression. An exaggerated, wavy platform and sculptural traction lugs raise you up and help keep you steady with standout traction.

Name: Run Star Motion CX Platform Workwear High Top
CONS Fastbreak Pro Mid Top
Description: BORN IN BASKETBALL, REIMAGINED FOR SKATEBOARDING. Originally released in '83, the Converse Fastbreak was front and centre on the basketball court. At the request of the CONS team, we've reimagined the OG model – this time, for skateboarding. Leather and nylon hold up to all-day sessions, while CONS traction rubber helps with grip and board feel.
